('c8bef4cd-96fa-5e68-934f-08c5c0156cc0', 'd405b8a1-0689-4401-a40d-d6a93d6d1611', 'I have an important meeting scheduled for tomorrow ___.', '我明天下午安排了一個重要的會議。', 'afternoon', 'morning', 'evening', 'night', 'after (在...之後) + noon (中午)', 'after (之後) + noon (中午) → 中午之後的時段。', '2026-07-06 18:47:29', '2026-07-06 18:47:29'),
