('20510bc2-43ed-5d31-be00-e5813af64df8', '4c3ab2db-b6a2-4bd6-ab05-17d977f13047', 'She was staring ___ the beautiful sunset in awe.', '她正驚嘆地凝視著美麗的日落。', 'at', 'to', 'for', 'with', '介系詞，與 stare 連用表示注視某物。', 'stare at 表示「凝視...」。', '2026-07-05 12:11:23', '2026-07-05 12:11:23'),
